snippet: The Boston Celtics may have crashed out of the playoffs after being pummeled by Atlanta on their home floor, but power forward Jonas Jerebko is not too down-hearted after finally getting a chance to show the Boston crowd what he can do as a starte...
lead_paragraph: The Boston Celtics may have crashed out of the playoffs after being pummeled by Atlanta on their home floor, but power forward Jonas Jerebko is not too down-hearted after finally getting a chance to show the Boston crowd what he can do as a starter.

headline.main: Celtics' Swede Jerebko Finishes Season Strong Despite Loss to Atlanta
headline.print_headline: Celtics' Swede Jerebko Finishes Season Strong Despite Loss to Atlanta
